# 零信任 A2A 机制

<div class="text-center text-lg mt-4 opacity-80">
Agent 调 Agent，每次都要证明身份 — 不存在长期信任密钥
</div>

```mermaid {scale: 0.6}
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Caller Agent
    participant IDP as IdP
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant T as Target Agent

    Note over C: client_assertion (JWT)<br/>iss/sub/aud/exp/jti · 60s
    Note over C: DPoP proof (JWT)<br/>htm/htu/iat/jti/jwk
    C->>IDP: POST /token/exchange
    IDP->>IDP: ① verify assertion sig (JWKS)
    IDP->>IDP: ② verify DPoP + jkt
    IDP->>IDP: ③ scope 三方求交
    IDP-->>C: access_token (cnf.jkt = thumbprint)<br/>120s · one-shot

    Note over C: 新 DPoP proof + ath=hash(token)
    C->>GW: /invoke + DPoP
    GW->>GW: JWT sig + jkt 匹配 + nonce 反重放
    GW->>T: 转发 (X-Target-Agent)
    T->>T: self-check (zero-trust)
    T-->>C: data
```

<div class="mt-2 text-xs opacity-60 text-center">
client_assertion 证身份 · one-shot token 防重放（sub_jti 绑定）· DPoP proof 防盗用
</div>

---
layout: two-cols
---

# 最小权限保证

<div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded bg-gray-50 font-mono text-sm">
effective_scope = <br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;callee_caps<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;∩ user_perms<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;∩ requested_scope
</div>

<div class="mt-4 text-sm space-y-2">

- **callee_caps**：被调用 Agent 的能力声明（capability YAML）
- **user_perms**：人类用户在 IdP 持有的权限
- **requested_scope**：本次任务请求的范围

</div>

<div class="mt-4 p-3 rounded bg-emerald-50 text-sm">
三者取交，最终令牌只持<strong>本次任务必需</strong>的最小可用权限
</div>

::right::

# 6 维度撤销

```python
revocation_sets = {
    "jti",     # 单个令牌
    "sub",     # 用户所有令牌
    "agent",   # Agent 所有令牌
    "trace",   # 一条调用链
    "plan",    # 一次 Plan 执行
    "chain",   # 委托链衍生
}
```

<div class="mt-4 text-sm">
撤销信号 → Redis Pub/Sub → 实时广播 Gateway，<strong>不依赖令牌过期</strong>。
</div>

<div class="mt-3 text-xs opacity-60">
粒度从单 token 到整条链路，事件响应可逐级收紧。
</div>

