# Orchestrator 调用链路

```mermaid {scale: 0.65}
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant DA as doc_assistant
    participant SDK as SDK Client
    participant IDP as IdP
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant DT as data_agent
    participant WB as web_agent

    U->>DA: POST /chat {query}
    DA->>DA: planner → DAG
    DA->>DA: plan_validate (capability/scope)
    Note over DA: dispatcher 拓扑分层
    par data 分支
        DA->>SDK: invoke(data_agent)
        SDK->>IDP: token-exchange (assertion + DPoP)
        IDP-->>SDK: 委托 token (cnf.jkt)
        SDK->>GW: /invoke + DPoP proof
        GW->>DT: 转发
        DT-->>SDK: {rows}
    and web 分支
        DA->>SDK: invoke(web_agent)
        SDK->>GW: /invoke (持新 token)
        GW->>WB: 转发
        WB-->>SDK: {summary}
    end
    DA->>DA: synthesizer (合并 + 二次过滤)
    DA->>DA: doc_writer → markdown/blocks
    DA-->>U: stream {answer, sources, doc_url}
```

<div class="mt-2 text-xs opacity-60 text-center">
同层无依赖节点并行执行 · 缩短整体任务耗时
</div>

---

# web_agent 四层安全防护

<div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-3 mt-6">

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-400">
<div class="font-bold text-red-700">① 网络层</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-3 space-y-1">
<div>SSRF + CIDR 黑名单</div>
<div>HTTPS-only · 禁 redirect</div>
<div>size / timeout 上限</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-400">
<div class="font-bold text-orange-700">② 解码层</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-3 space-y-1">
<div>四级 charset 探测</div>
<div>三启发式 mojibake 检测</div>
<div>乱码注入在字节阶段剥掉</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400">
<div class="font-bold text-amber-700">③ 清洗层</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-3 space-y-1">
<div>同管线 <code>_extract_text</code></div>
<div>用于 search snippet + HTML</div>
<div>剥脚本 / 事件 / 标签 / JS</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 border-l-4 border-emerald-400">
<div class="font-bold text-emerald-700">④ LLM 层</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-3 space-y-1">
<div>system prompt 禁执行嵌入指令</div>
<div>raw text 不出库</div>
<div>synthesizer 二次过滤</div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="mt-8 p-3 rounded bg-slate-50 text-xs text-center">
Prompt Injection 防御 = <strong>纵深</strong>：网络 → 解码 → 清洗 → LLM，任一层独立失效都不致破防
</div>

