# 四、SDK · 客户端基座

---

# SDK 核心功能

<div class="text-sm opacity-70 mt-2">Agents 架构接入 A2A-Token-system 的统一客户端 — 屏蔽 DPoP / Token Exchange 复杂度</div>

<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200">
<div class="font-bold">📞 调用接口 <code>client.invoke()</code></div>
<div class="text-xs mt-2">串联 IdP + Gateway 验证 → 调用 Agent 执行任务，单方法封装全链路</div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-green-50 border border-green-200">
<div class="font-bold">📜 Assertion 自签</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-2">生成代理身份证明：<code>iss / sub / aud / exp / jti</code>，RSA-2048 签发</div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 border border-purple-200">
<div class="font-bold">🔐 DPoP Proof 签名</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-2">绑定访问令牌：<code>htm / htu / iat / jti / ath</code>，公钥拇指印写入 <code>cnf.jkt</code></div>
</div>

<div class="p-4 rounded-lg bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200">
<div class="font-bold">🔌 Adapter 多框架接入</div>
<div class="text-xs mt-2">
<code>LangGraph</code> 节点 · <code>LangChain</code> StructuredTool · <code>AutoGen</code> ConversableAgent —— 三套 adapter
</div>
</div>

</div>

<div class="mt-6">

```python {3-7}
# 一行 invoke，背后全部完成
async def invoke(self, *, target, intent, on_behalf_of,
                 purpose="", plan_id=None, task_id=None,
                 trace_id=None, idempotency_key=None):
    assertion = self._sign_assertion(target)        # RFC 7523
    dpop = self._sign_dpop(htu, htm)                # RFC 9449
    token = await self._idp_exchange(assertion, dpop)  # RFC 8693
    return await self._gateway_invoke(token, intent)
```

</div>

